data.name: Garlic and Herb Guacamole
data.quickTastyDescription: A creamy and flavorful avocado dip infused with garlic and fresh herbs, perfect for chips or as a topping.
detailedCookingInstructions: Cut the avocados in half, remove the pit and scoop the flesh into a mixing bowl.
Add fresh lime juice, minced garlic, chopped cilantro, and chopped parsley to the bowl.
Mash the avocado mixture with a fork until you reach your desired level of creaminess.
Season with salt and black pepper to taste.
Serve immediately with tortilla chips or as a topping for your favorite dishes.
data.modifiersForBase: Garlic and fresh herbs added for flavor
